                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">AutoScroll</td><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">bool</td><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">true</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground">Sticks to the bottom when new content arrives, using a MutationObserver.</td></tr>
